{"tid":883602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨行飛鵝山　女子迷路失蹤","createTime":"2018-10-31T03:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T13:01:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0b260ee4b62ed83e12a9a87ca0044f14ac02b15c","tid":883602,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181031/20534725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181031%2F20534725&d=8px2%2Fe9R3OJ8fqB58kdGNEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d353a55f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181031%2F20534725&h=3dcb76e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181031/20534725</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月31日 <br />\n<br />\n獨行飛鵝山　女子迷路失蹤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181031/large/31lp6p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181031%2Flarge%2F31lp6p7.jpg&h=c156d66d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批搜救人員昨到飛鵝山搜索失蹤行山女子。張培生攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名25歲女子前晚獨自到飛鵝山行山，其間疑迷路撥打「112」求救，之後電話斷線失去聯絡。搜救人員隨即登山搜救，直升機亦出動協助，但搜索超過一日仍未有發現，搜救行動至今日凌晨仍然繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾撥打112求救<br />\n<br />\n事發於周一傍晚6時許，警方接獲25歲女事主報警求助，指自己獨自上飛鵝山但迷路。消防員接報上山搜索，政府飛行服務隊亦派直升機，在高空用探射燈照向山頭搜索，至凌晨時分仍無發現。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，女事主用手機按112緊急求助電話報警，自稱在飛鵝山行山迷途，但講話途中她一度沒有回應，又稱電話電力不足，之後便斷線失去聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n昨早9時許，警方、消防員及民安隊大批搜救人員，在札山道臨時指揮中心集合後，繼續登山搜救失蹤女事主，直升機亦到場在半空盤旋協助搜索。至中午時分，大批警方機動部隊警員加入搜山。至今日凌晨搜救行動仍然繼續。<br />\n<br />\n行山人士在香港境內用手機撥打112，會轉駁至警方999指揮及控制中心，即使是在流動電話網絡訊號微弱的郊區，只要所處位置有任何一個本地流動電話網絡覆蓋就可撥打。<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑稱，由於女事主失去聯絡前曾打出求救電話，即使之後電話無電，亦可憑其最後手機訊號，透過網絡商或手機GPS定位系統確定女事主失蹤前的大概位置。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張培生、姜偉康  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n七旬翁涉多次非禮11歲女<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n擺街站大巡遊星級議員站台　泛民周末晒冷撐李卓人"},{"pid":"667864e141a8aeccb213bf23f3fce233b87c8583","tid":883602,"uid":19712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"仲未搵到? 會唔會已經返左屋企?"},{"pid":"bbf23a08fb093f50fbfd60a2cf5dde550fdf407b","tid":883602,"uid":52221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T03:55:58.000Z","msg":"飛鵝山都可以迷路失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffedf472737734fbf88ae53514ff3b5a2c8b22e5","tid":883602,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"聽到好悽厲慘叫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd72d6c76dc1ce81137d1e2694e2d4e39be2bbe1","tid":883602,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f345c69398310716603ca12fdf3f991e966376f","tid":883602,"uid":48918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:16:57.000Z","msg":"仲未搵到?"},{"pid":"90d973267df55dfe786b19c6edf60c715ca5c8d6","tid":883602,"uid":79427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:26:41.000Z","msg":"入結界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c8d90c7545c9cf5e1b095ff5fb0738e65563b3","tid":883602,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:29:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會又入左鵝肚。。。<br />\n<br />\n個邊好難行下bo"},{"pid":"8dbc18fbec801074e49e9008236994cdd2385b53","tid":883602,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"唔怪得尋日晏晝咁嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c92a0b24973e7914245c107da4b6fe4ede9a49","tid":883602,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:30:34.000Z","msg"